Feature: POST Account Authorized
  As a admin
  I want to take user account
  So I can update some user account

  Scenario: Update user account with valid data to update new book list
    Given I set url and valid user account
    When I request with valid user account and update user new book list
    Then I get status code 200

    Scenario: Update user account with valid data to update book title
      Given I set url and valid user data
      When I request with valid user data and update book title
      Then I obtain status code 200
